&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sect1&#34;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;_customer_relationship_model_crm&#34;&gt;Customer Relationship Model CRM&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sectionbody&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;imageblock kroki&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://kroki.io/plantuml/svg/eNqVVdtO4zAQfe9X-BHKwgegqAIK0lZiYVX2HU3tIbVw7Mhxd6mg_77TxEl9SWE3D210ZuacGXtmctU4sG5TqcmkBv4KJbKnNVgUrCiWyB3oUuFsxt4njB6pHdoX4Mi-Q7MQHt0_T85KXTIpTk5TTEOFHt1NcppHGfIoQxFmoBkL-AVlw97HLHNTVajdEevjH43WS-3aX69efFxcDA5p4J120m2DDM_6uhy-uaDaM3ZvOKhbcMherKn2L0fMzgTGPJVOsocXo2h7CCP4cAShrTXCqnEWuGNcQdN406KqoxM5oNPzc0Yi7JI5khoxeiVy4F4zcArlKaDLoBPekxaFRW6smM1CS88YJtRjSTpB1A3o17nRmppVGk3UJ8tvxvK1FKesVxlp1BXoFFtJnrnphkrYOAy7sdO9FsIi_beC7GtFOn1El6LUQ6gFihSvzY15y8HGcSMwxdW-s_omCHCLJR1JinKz0c5u84ruKpDqf8sShqJ0rsxlLenicpWfa6Pxwf6zgN5UKxrLjmd3WFM3VAYd3PNtm8DzfPkjW1lHRjlKZ24rj8uqVtgNT-IZzdsQELLcYwkq5zmQ91QHpCUL4kK6B3AbOxAeiY2c4nusldkifp7J4GVotGKuzJyliXQr7Jom7jdBc2rJZGgJKD4oMHSJhsfjUdgATpPIdsfEBDTx3TaLdT2Y5EzxDSrlu-grLwxKXOybB9rN8kmViVeYZ2CKgkN8mlP0FY-5Dsd0yaB7lUgbka71ilYJfcr_Ann5V1w=&#34; alt=&#34;bus-crmRealm-uml&#34;/&gt;
